title: Post so I can see your FEK and I...
body:
Will rate it
Tell you what I think about it
Comment on how nicely/badly it fits your Summoner name
I'll also want to see how many referential ones I recognize

Yeah in the end, sorry, I just ended looking at your name and FEK and saying what went through my mind, and built a little story about what I saw from your avatar and name. Cool stuff.

Thanks for the replies

Hehe, 1000 views, feels good.
Although half the comments are by me, doh.

RIP Green Shrek Sion
